00:20:11,000 --> 00:20:12,790
Should Your Majesty
show leniency this time,

278
00:20:13,000 --> 00:20:14,990
how shall Your Majesty
uphold Qi's moral integrity?

279
00:20:15,200 --> 00:20:17,280
And how shall Qi uphold
Your Majesty's honor?

280
00:20:18,120 --> 00:20:19,240
Everything I've done

281
00:20:19,560 --> 00:20:21,320
is for the country and for Your Majesty.

282
00:20:21,620 --> 00:20:23,400
I ask that Your Majesty
judge with clarity.

283
00:20:29,920 --> 00:20:33,080
Chancellor Shen worked hard for Qi.

284
00:20:34,480 --> 00:20:35,240
How

285
00:20:35,760 --> 00:20:37,520
could I misunderstand you?

286
00:20:43,480 --> 00:20:44,880
Don't talk nonsense.

287
00:21:04,320 --> 00:21:05,320
The Meng family

288
00:21:05,840 --> 00:21:08,720
instigated Prince Wugou
to commit such a heinous crime.

289
00:21:10,240 --> 00:21:11,520
They should be severely punished,

290
00:21:13,760 --> 00:21:14,360
but

291
00:21:15,960 --> 00:21:17,000
this is a serious matter.

292
00:21:19,480 --> 00:21:20,600
Let me think about it.

293
00:21:57,010 --> 00:21:57,730
Right Chancellor.

294
00:21:57,740 --> 00:21:58,990
- Right Chancellor.
- Right Chancellor.

295
00:21:59,800 --> 00:22:01,120
You traveled all the way here,

296
00:22:01,720 --> 00:22:03,600
but it seems
that you're still a step too late.

297
00:22:05,040 --> 00:22:06,240
In the past, all these people

298
00:22:06,600 --> 00:22:08,000
flattered you.

299
00:22:08,240 --> 00:22:10,160
But today, they're trying to avoid you.

300
00:22:11,280 --> 00:22:13,400
I really feel sorry for you.

301
00:22:16,520 --> 00:22:18,200
There's no need for pretenses

302
00:22:19,080 --> 00:22:21,160
between us.

303
00:22:23,040 --> 00:22:24,520
The outcome on the battlefield

304
00:22:25,000 --> 00:22:27,620
has never been decided by the loss
or gain of a city or stronghold.

305
00:22:28,480 --> 00:22:29,520
The same goes for court.

306
00:22:30,360 --> 00:22:31,960
The east wind may prevail for now,

307
00:22:32,520 --> 00:22:33,440
but who's to know

308
00:22:33,920 --> 00:22:34,800
whether

309
00:22:35,720 --> 00:22:38,280
the west wind
won't turn the tide one day?

310
00:22:40,800 --> 00:22:41,600
I'll just wait

311
00:22:43,640 --> 00:22:44,760
for your downfall.

312
00:22:46,560 --> 00:22:47,640
Likewise.

313
00:23:31,480 --> 00:23:32,120
Father.

314
00:23:41,720 --> 00:23:42,640
You've suffered.

315
00:23:46,400 --> 00:23:47,680
Even imprisoned,

316
00:23:48,600 --> 00:23:50,560
you didn't lament or resent.

317
00:23:51,600 --> 00:23:53,440
You're indeed
a descendant of the Meng family.

318
00:23:57,080 --> 00:23:58,640
I failed you.

319
00:23:59,520 --> 00:24:00,840
I failed to protect Prince Wugou.

320
00:24:04,560 --> 00:24:05,640
You did nothing wrong.

321
00:24:07,720 --> 00:24:08,760
The mistake was

322
00:24:09,720 --> 00:24:10,840
the Meng family's misfortune

323
00:24:11,680 --> 00:24:13,560
to have such an incompetent

324
00:24:13,920 --> 00:24:16,840
and self-willed fool like your cousin.

325
00:24:18,180 --> 00:24:20,680
Incapable of success, yet more
than capable of causing failure.

326
00:24:23,320 --> 00:24:25,000
All the Meng family's

327
00:24:25,440 --> 00:24:26,800
years of effort

328
00:24:28,200 --> 00:24:29,800
is ruined overnight.

329
00:24:35,420 --> 00:24:36,640
Prince Wugou has been deposed?

330
00:24:40,040 --> 00:24:40,880
That's right.

331
00:24:42,600 --> 00:24:44,840
I rushed back to Yujing,

332
00:24:45,360 --> 00:24:46,880
but it's all settled

333
00:24:47,400 --> 00:24:48,560
and irreversible.

334
00:24:49,480 --> 00:24:50,400
If I had known,

335
00:24:52,520 --> 00:24:53,880
I'd have risked my life

336
00:24:55,000 --> 00:24:57,400
to stop Prince Wugou
from acting recklessly.

337
00:25:00,000 --> 00:25:01,760
Even if this didn't happen,

338
00:25:02,440 --> 00:25:04,200
there would be other things.

339
00:25:05,440 --> 00:25:07,280
Prince Wugou
is unworthy of great duties.

340
00:25:09,560 --> 00:25:10,640
But Huaijin,

341
00:25:11,440 --> 00:25:13,280
because of Prince Wugou,

342
00:25:13,800 --> 00:25:15,090
the Meng family can be said to be

343
00:25:15,880 --> 00:25:17,280
surrounded by a pack of wolves.

344
00:25:18,160 --> 00:25:19,320
We're hanging by a thread.

345
00:25:21,240 --> 00:25:22,520
Everyone's waiting

346
00:25:23,080 --> 00:25:24,480
to pounce

347
00:25:24,920 --> 00:25:26,360
at our mistake

348
00:25:26,840 --> 00:25:28,960
and shatter the Meng family.

349
00:25:31,480 --> 00:25:32,380
We mustn't be the ones

350
00:25:34,280 --> 00:25:37,080
to cause the Meng family's downfall.

351
00:25:40,520 --> 00:25:41,680
That's why

352
00:25:42,360 --> 00:25:44,320
we need to settle this
as soon as possible

353
00:25:44,420 --> 00:25:46,680
so that the Meng family
can distance ourselves from this

354
00:25:48,400 --> 00:25:51,800
and await the right moment.

355
00:25:55,520 --> 00:25:56,520
Do you understand?

356
00:26:08,160 --> 00:26:11,120
Having enjoyed the Meng family's
care and honor since childhood,

357
00:26:12,400 --> 00:26:13,680
it's only right that I repay them

358
00:26:14,400 --> 00:26:15,640
in their time of crisis.

359
00:26:17,840 --> 00:26:18,960
I understand.

360
00:26:24,600 --> 00:26:25,400
But Father,

361
00:26:27,800 --> 00:26:29,200
I only have one request.

362
00:26:32,400 --> 00:26:32,880
Go ahead.

363
00:26:37,800 --> 00:26:40,320
Zhenzhen is in a difficult situation
at Chancellor Residence.

364
00:26:41,480 --> 00:26:42,480
As her older brother,

365
00:26:43,000 --> 00:26:44,800
I haven't been able
to take care of her much.

366
00:26:47,920 --> 00:26:48,920
After this,

367
00:26:52,320 --> 00:26:54,520
let her live a easier life.

368
00:26:59,960 --> 00:27:00,760
Don't worry.

369
00:27:03,480 --> 00:27:04,520
No matter what,

370
00:27:06,260 --> 00:27:08,480
Zhenzhen is still
the Meng family's legitimate daughter.

371
00:27:10,400 --> 00:27:11,960
I won't let others

372
00:27:13,280 --> 00:27:14,560
bully her.

373
00:27:22,520 --> 00:27:23,120
Father.

374
00:27:25,560 --> 00:27:26,480
I'm unfilial

375
00:27:29,000 --> 00:27:30,880
for not being able
to take care of you anymore.

376
00:27:53,680 --> 00:27:54,320
Get up.

377
00:28:08,840 --> 00:28:09,720
Huaijin.

378
00:28:12,440 --> 00:28:14,640
The Meng family is proud of you.

379
00:29:24,080 --> 00:29:25,000
The moon

380
00:29:28,600 --> 00:29:29,560
is beautiful.

381
00:29:30,780 --> 00:29:34,140
(Shen Residence)

382
00:29:35,520 --> 00:29:36,320
(Zhenzhen.)

383
00:29:37,880 --> 00:29:39,600
(When you see this letter,)

384
00:29:40,760 --> 00:29:42,320
(I should be gone.)

385
00:29:45,640 --> 00:29:46,800
(God's will is uncertain.)

386
00:29:47,360 --> 00:29:48,480
(The world is ever drifting)

387
00:29:48,960 --> 00:29:50,080
(and unpredictable.)

388
00:29:51,160 --> 00:29:53,360
(Fame and career are empty in the end.)

389
00:29:54,540 --> 00:29:56,240
(Fortunately,
my parents are still alive.)

390
00:29:56,410 --> 00:29:57,990
(And I have my wife and younger sister.)

391
00:29:59,040 --> 00:30:01,720
(If I can save my clan with my life,)

392
00:30:02,560 --> 00:30:04,000
(I'll rest)

393
00:30:04,400 --> 00:30:05,520
(in peace.)

394
00:30:06,960 --> 00:30:08,320
(However,)

395
00:30:08,800 --> 00:30:10,960
(thinking of your situation
in Chancellor Residence,)

396
00:30:12,440 --> 00:30:14,920
(I'm afraid I won't have the chance
to take care of you again.)

397
00:30:17,800 --> 00:30:19,440
(Don't go to extremes.)

398
00:30:20,120 --> 00:30:22,360
(Chancellor Shen isn't the kind
to drive others to ruin.)

399
00:30:23,560 --> 00:30:24,800
(Father also promised me)

400
00:30:25,840 --> 00:30:27,360
(to take good care of you.)

401
00:30:29,200 --> 00:30:30,240
(This way,)

402
00:30:31,480 --> 00:30:33,480
(I have no regrets.)

403
00:30:33,480 --> 00:30:35,520
(Meng Huaijin's Final Letter)

404
00:30:35,520 --> 00:30:36,240
Madam.

405
00:30:37,000 --> 00:30:38,960
Let me put the letter away for you.

406
00:30:42,760 --> 00:30:45,120
If I had known that day
was the last time we would meet,

407
00:30:47,760 --> 00:30:50,480
I would have disobeyed orders to see him.

408
00:31:00,880 --> 00:31:02,160
It's a pity that Huaijin

409
00:31:03,560 --> 00:31:05,480
didn't get to drink that bowl of soup.

410
00:31:11,120 --> 00:31:11,960
Madam.

411
00:31:13,160 --> 00:31:14,640
At least you bid goodbye

412
00:31:16,160 --> 00:31:17,520
to Mr. Meng with a smile.

413
00:31:24,240 --> 00:31:25,240
I didn't expect

414
00:31:27,120 --> 00:31:28,640
Father to sacrifice

415
00:31:28,960 --> 00:31:30,240
even his own son

416
00:31:31,000 --> 00:31:32,960
just to save the family.

417
00:31:36,160 --> 00:31:38,520
Huaijin seems to be
the son of a noble family,

418
00:31:40,200 --> 00:31:42,480
but he's just a pawn
to pave the way for the family.

419
00:31:46,600 --> 00:31:47,920
I'm the same.

420
00:31:49,280 --> 00:31:51,480
All the Meng family members
are the same.

421
00:31:53,880 --> 00:31:55,720
Even Father isn't immune.

422
00:31:59,200 --> 00:32:00,960
Being a father

423
00:32:01,600 --> 00:32:04,580
is less important than the patriarch
of the Meng family and Right Chancellor.

424
00:32:05,500 --> 00:32:07,800
The will of the noble family
determines Father's actions.

425
00:32:09,800 --> 00:32:10,720
One day,

426
00:32:12,240 --> 00:32:14,120
I will also be sacrificed
in the same way.

427
00:32:15,840 --> 00:32:16,560
Madam.

428
00:32:17,440 --> 00:32:18,520
Life is short.

429
00:32:19,680 --> 00:32:20,720
Why worry

430
00:32:20,720 --> 00:32:22,320
about something that hasn't happened?

431
00:32:24,480 --> 00:32:26,720
Mr. Meng wants you to live well.

432
00:32:35,320 --> 00:32:36,160
You're right.

433
00:32:39,040 --> 00:32:40,440
I want to live well.

434
00:32:41,840 --> 00:32:43,960
Someone, come!

435
00:32:44,280 --> 00:32:45,560
Mr. Meng committed suicide!

436
00:32:50,580 --> 00:32:55,860
(Confession Letter)

437
00:33:00,880 --> 00:33:01,800
The Meng family

438
00:33:02,440 --> 00:33:03,800
has been loyal for generations.

439
00:33:04,400 --> 00:33:05,120
I never thought

440
00:33:05,840 --> 00:33:08,240
my son to make such a big mistake.

441
00:33:08,920 --> 00:33:09,990
A child's lack of discipline

442
00:33:10,320 --> 00:33:11,320
is the father's fault.

443
00:33:12,000 --> 00:33:12,520
I'm

444
00:33:13,400 --> 00:33:14,600
ashamed to face Your Majesty.

445
00:33:15,160 --> 00:33:16,720
I'm ashamed to face my ancestors.

446
00:33:17,240 --> 00:33:19,760
I no longer have the face
to serve Your Majesty.

447
00:33:20,560 --> 00:33:21,600
I hope Your Majesty

448
00:33:22,280 --> 00:33:24,120
can show mercy and compassion.

449
00:33:25,320 --> 00:33:26,360
Allow me

450
00:33:27,080 --> 00:33:28,520
to beg for my son's remains

451
00:33:29,360 --> 00:33:30,640
so that we can

452
00:33:32,000 --> 00:33:33,640
to retire to the countryside together.

453
00:33:38,920 --> 00:33:39,800
Right Chancellor.

454
00:33:41,120 --> 00:33:42,000
No.

455
00:33:43,680 --> 00:33:45,360
The court is in need of capable people.

456
00:33:46,040 --> 00:33:49,120
How can you choose your household
over the country?

457
00:33:50,840 --> 00:33:52,200
If we follow your logic,

458
00:33:53,280 --> 00:33:54,520
Prince Wugou's sin

459
00:33:54,680 --> 00:33:55,880
is all because

460
00:33:55,880 --> 00:33:57,520
of my failure as a father.

461
00:33:58,120 --> 00:33:58,720
Do you

462
00:33:59,040 --> 00:34:01,360
want me to issue
a decree of guilt against myself?

463
00:34:01,640 --> 00:34:02,840
I have no such intention.

464
00:34:04,840 --> 00:34:05,440
It's just

465
00:34:06,720 --> 00:34:07,280
that

466
00:34:08,320 --> 00:34:09,560
I'm old and weak.

467
00:34:10,360 --> 00:34:11,840
I also have no ambition.

468
00:34:12,040 --> 00:34:13,600
If I remain in court,

469
00:34:14,080 --> 00:34:17,400
I fear others
will accuse me of being power-hungry.

470
00:34:22,480 --> 00:34:24,160
My reputation is nothing.

471
00:34:25,240 --> 00:34:26,600
If this matter

472
00:34:27,200 --> 00:34:28,240
implicates Your Majesty

473
00:34:28,600 --> 00:34:29,720
another charge

474
00:34:30,000 --> 00:34:31,640
of misjudgment,

475
00:34:31,640 --> 00:34:32,360
I

476
00:34:33,560 --> 00:34:34,880
will be guilty of a serious crime.

477
00:34:35,840 --> 00:34:37,280
No need to say more.

478
00:34:38,880 --> 00:34:39,840
Your petition

479
00:34:40,280 --> 00:34:41,640
to resign

480
00:34:42,120 --> 00:34:42,920
is

481
00:34:44,400 --> 00:34:45,480
hereby denied.

482
00:34:52,320 --> 00:34:53,280
Right Chancellor.

483
00:34:54,480 --> 00:34:55,680
The Meng family

484
00:34:56,200 --> 00:34:57,640
has thrived for a century.

485
00:34:58,060 --> 00:34:59,490
You're deeply rooted and flourishing.

486
00:34:59,960 --> 00:35:01,440
Even if you have some rotten apples,

487
00:35:01,600 --> 00:35:03,280
just remove them.

488
00:35:03,800 --> 00:35:05,240
Why destroy the whole clan

489
00:35:05,320 --> 00:35:06,520
because of one person's fault?

490
00:35:08,640 --> 00:35:09,520
My dear chancellor.

491
00:35:10,720 --> 00:35:12,200
The court is hectic.

492
00:35:13,680 --> 00:35:15,000
I still need you

493
00:35:15,280 --> 00:35:17,880
to share some of the burden for me.

494
00:35:23,600 --> 00:35:24,240
I'm

495
00:35:25,640 --> 00:35:28,520
willing to lay down my life
for Your Majesty

496
00:35:29,080 --> 00:35:30,320
without hesitation.

497
00:35:39,160 --> 00:35:39,920
My dear chancellor.

498
00:35:41,240 --> 00:35:42,200
My condolences.

499
00:35:55,840 --> 00:35:58,120
Chancellor,
we've put so much effort into this.

500
00:35:58,130 --> 00:36:00,080
You even put yourself
at the heart of the scheme,

501
00:36:00,080 --> 00:36:01,850
but we still
can't overthrow the Meng family.

502
00:36:01,860 --> 00:36:03,540
Why did His Majesty
handle it in this way?

503
00:36:05,400 --> 00:36:06,840
His Majesty is reminding me

504
00:36:07,200 --> 00:36:09,040
I'm just a blade he forged.

505
00:36:10,480 --> 00:36:12,200
I can only cut

506
00:36:12,840 --> 00:36:14,680
as much as he allows.

507
00:36:16,560 --> 00:36:17,560
What's next then?

508
00:36:18,310 --> 00:36:19,090
It doesn't matter.

509
00:36:20,240 --> 00:36:22,240
Even a centipede moves after death.

510
00:36:22,800 --> 00:36:25,600
Not to mention the top noble family.

511
00:36:27,000 --> 00:36:29,200
Now that they lost
Prince Wugou and Meng Huaijin,

512
00:36:29,840 --> 00:36:31,600
the Meng family
has suffered a severe blow.

513
00:36:33,040 --> 00:36:35,200
I have plenty of time to play with them.

514
00:36:38,140 --> 00:36:39,480
We're a newly opened pastry shop.

515
00:36:39,480 --> 00:36:40,760
Authentic Beiyuan specialties.

516
00:36:40,760 --> 00:36:43,040
They're all delicious.
Limited quantity daily.

517
00:36:43,640 --> 00:36:44,880
- I want some.
- I want some.

518
00:36:44,880 --> 00:36:45,400
Come here.

519
00:36:45,400 --> 00:36:46,360
Line up.

520
00:36:46,660 --> 00:36:49,340
Everyone line up. If you don't line up,
I'm not selling any to you.

521
00:36:49,400 --> 00:36:50,480
Line up.

522
00:36:57,000 --> 00:36:58,860
Your Highness,
it's time to take your medicine.

523
00:36:59,680 --> 00:37:00,600
Leave it there first.

524
00:37:09,040 --> 00:37:09,640
Your Highness.

525
00:37:09,960 --> 00:37:11,560
I heard that Madam Meng's brother

526
00:37:11,600 --> 00:37:13,120
committed suicide in prison.

527
00:37:15,880 --> 00:37:16,800
In that case,

528
00:37:17,640 --> 00:37:19,080
Chancellor's plan succeeded.

529
00:37:23,360 --> 00:37:24,480
Qing must have heard about

530
00:37:25,720 --> 00:37:27,680
the news of Prince Wugou's deposition

531
00:37:28,600 --> 00:37:30,040
and Meng Huaijin's suicide in prison.

532
00:37:31,000 --> 00:37:31,720
Right now,

533
00:37:32,000 --> 00:37:33,200
she must be angry at me

534
00:37:33,200 --> 00:37:35,040
for not delivering the news sooner.

535
00:37:36,060 --> 00:37:38,300
Deliver this letter to Yang Wanqing
as soon as possible.

536
00:37:38,680 --> 00:37:39,560
Don't worry.

537
00:37:39,600 --> 00:37:41,990
Recently, getting in and out
has gotten a lot easier for me.

538
00:37:42,020 --> 00:37:44,280
So long as I claim
that you want some pastries or snacks,

539
00:37:44,280 --> 00:37:45,480
they'll let me out.

540
00:37:45,840 --> 00:37:47,160
He's not completely heartless.

541
00:37:48,080 --> 00:37:49,280
Don't let your guard down.

542
00:37:50,720 --> 00:37:52,160
I got involved defenseless.

543
00:37:52,640 --> 00:37:54,000
One wrong move,

544
00:37:54,100 --> 00:37:55,640
and the consequences will be disastrous.

545
00:37:57,040 --> 00:37:57,600
Go now.

546
00:37:58,120 --> 00:37:58,480
Alright.

547
00:38:27,800 --> 00:38:28,560
Chancellor.

548
00:38:30,840 --> 00:38:32,960
Do you want me to tell Her Highness
that you're here?

549
00:38:32,960 --> 00:38:34,680
No need. I'm leaving.

550
00:38:36,560 --> 00:38:37,510
We bought some pastries

551
00:38:37,840 --> 00:38:39,160
for her Highness on our way back.

552
00:38:40,160 --> 00:38:40,680
By the way,

553
00:38:41,200 --> 00:38:42,120
His Majesty will hold

554
00:38:42,120 --> 00:38:43,990
a modest tea banquet in the palace
in ten days.

555
00:38:44,800 --> 00:38:46,480
If Her Highness is bored,

556
00:38:47,320 --> 00:38:48,000
tell Zhan Lu.

